      <title>美国债券收益率飙升促使一些公司推迟债务销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/handful-of-companies-delay-selling-bonds-in-us-as-yields-climb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，美国高等级公司债收益率攀升至接近去年年中以来的最高水平，推高了潜在的借贷成本，因此少数公司暂停出售这些债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/handful-of-companies-delay-selling-bonds-in-us-as-yields-climb</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 19:19:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
