      <title>灾难援助缓解洛杉矶地区市政债券的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/disaster-aid-seen-easing-risk-to-los-angeles-area-muni-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[FHN Financial 的一份报告称，由于美国官员承诺联邦紧急事务管理局将提供资金支持，洛杉矶毁灭性的山火不太可能对地方政府债券产生影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/disaster-aid-seen-easing-risk-to-los-angeles-area-muni-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 19:06:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税担忧引发白银和铜市场脱节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/trump-tariff-fears-spark-disconnect-in-silver-and-copper-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易员加大对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 将对金属征收高额进口关税的押注，作为其全球贸易战升级的一部分，纽约的铜和白银期货价格飙升至竞争对手的国际价格基准之上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/trump-tariff-fears-spark-disconnect-in-silver-and-copper-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 18:30:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
